🚗 Hi! We're Corey & Kharma! 🚗

🌟 About Us 🌟
Welcome to our family-owned and operated small car rental business. With a shared passion for adventure and a love for all things automotive, we embarked on this journey to provide you with more than just a car rental service – we offer you the keys to unforgettable memories.

bio.employment: Every day from ground up building an ENGLISH EMPIRE in rental vehicles and sweat hoods only to remind you of an ENGLISH experience.
bio.openEndedText: Hi guys, I’m your host Mr. English and thanks for stopping by my page of ENGLISH MOTOS. Here you’ll find my 1st & hopefully several more selective well maintained trending colorful rentals. I too have rented many of vehicles and thought how I could service customers in such ways as I hoped to be serviced. So here I am, first handed, giving you a well cleaned and safe rental with many features to enjoy your trip. All I ask is you follow the TURO guidelines and treat this vehicle as if you were expecting to rent again and would like to receive it in the same shape and conditions as you have when the keys were given. Please no smoking as it’s a rental violation and a violation to others who don’t smoke.  I too am human and tend to forget policies put in place to keep order but now that I have the chance to run a business I see what hard work it takes to remind myself of the importance that’s needed to keep customers safe & happy. So help me, help you, help others to making this a win win experience.

🚗 Hosting on Turo for 2+ Year
Embarking on Turo hosting over the past year has been an incredible journey, marked by over 236+ trip reviews completed with an exceptional 4.95 rating. This tenure has equipped me with an acute understanding of guests' needs, ensuring a smooth and enjoyable rental experience. My dedication to Turo hosting has been unwavering, ensuring that each guest receives the highest quality service.

🌟 Over 2 Years as a Host on Multiple Platforms
Having honed my hosting skills across various platforms for more than two years, I've cultivated a profound expertise in providing top-notch experiences for renters. This wealth of experience guarantees a seamless and professional rental process, making every guest feel valued and taken care of from the moment they book.

🚀 Growing Fleet & Expanded Options
The vision for my Turo fleet is expansive. In 2024, we're planning to introduce four additional vehicles, diversifying our offerings to cater to every customer's distinct preferences. Whether it's an economical choice or an adrenaline-pumping sports car, I am committed to providing an array of options that meet and exceed every guest's expectations.

🌟 Stellar 5-Star Reviews
The testimonials from satisfied customers serve as a testament to my unwavering commitment to ensuring a flawless rental experience. Each 5-star review is a badge of honor, earned through consistent dedication to customer satisfaction, responsiveness, and attention to detail.

🏆 Top All-Star Host in the Queen City
Being recognized as one of the top hosts in Charlotte is a result of my commitment to growth, efficiency, and retaining happy customers. My success is rooted in an earnest desire to continuously improve, ensuring that each guest not only returns but also recommends my services to others.

Visit my website at www.eliteenterprisesllc.net to explore my entire Turo fleet! My commitment to excellence in service delivery ensures that choosing me as your host guarantees an exceptional and unforgettable rental experience. 🔗

We are excited to offer you a 5-star experience!  I have worked as an automotive engineer both for a manufacturer and for a race team, and I will ensure that our fleet is in excellent condition for your trip.  When I am not working, you will find me autocrossing my Miata or spending time with my family.

I am in love with the affordability & convenience of this car! It makes my adventures a breeze. I love laying the back down and being able to star gaze or watch a movie all while in the comfort of the car! This is a great car to utilize for a day trip to Asheville, or just to get from point A to B.

As a licensed automotive dealer, I find repossessed vehicles at dealer auctions that need light reconditioning and maintenance for thousands under market value. Then, I turn them into reliable rental vehicles and pass the savings we got, onto you. 

By avoiding retail dealerships and financing, I am able to price our cars cheaper than the competition. This also allows us to stay profitable, maintain our vehicles to last, and hire a full support team to ensure customer satisfaction throughout your rental experience. 

With my average vehicle purchase being under $5000...our vehicles are not pretty, flashy, and surely not going to impress anyone. That being said: I am sure that you will get the most affordable and reliable vehicle to handle all your personal or business needs.

I appreciate you taking the time to learn more about my business model. My team and I look forward to give you an affordable and reliable rental experience in the near future!
